      "community": "Jain Resource Recycling Ltd : A metal recycling compounder in the making",
      "timestamp": "2026-05-18T12:39:47.408Z",
      "text": "Q4 results are out. Not sure how to read through the results as while topline growth continues there is a significant decline in margins (QoQ). Based on segmental results, copper and copper ingots division seems to be the sole culprit. Not sure why did the margins decline there when copper prices are hitting new highs daily. bseindia.com 8ea95c49-d937-42bb-9bce-6bf52a44356f.pdf",
